s&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;Induction says that prediction is the main reason science exists, but it&amp;rsquo;s really explanation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
